{"tid":1545291,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"每日19:01播歌","createTime":"2019-09-06T00:57:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-06T00:57:27.000Z","uid":73194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"d3deefab3080d8cea4725f63121d957be60ae33b","tid":1545291,"uid":73194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T00:57:27.000Z","msg":"既然每日cctvb會係1830播新聞前奏國歌，我地都一樣可以做，或者開民間記者會前都可以播歌<br />\n<br />\n不論你身在何處何地，只要時間搭正1901分就開大你既手機聲音播以下歌<br />\n<br />\n選擇1901係因為1/7係今次運動既一個重大時刻<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/y7yRDOLCy4Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fy7yRDOLCy4Y&d=qjQisgq6tteJ1Wb%2FuF84H%2BDT5CHOggjCyLUuLmpgHOg%3D&h=f597f15c\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/y7yRDOLCy4Y</a><br />\n<br />\n播歌時，可以選擇默站既形式表示尊重，又可以細細聲跟住唱<br />\n<br />\n個意義同每日2200大叫一樣，但我相信呢個做法更不會惹人反感<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}